  <brief_title>Treatment of Pemphigus Patients With Rituximab 1000mgX2 and Assessment of Immune Status Via Cylex</brief_title>
  <official_title>Treatment of Moderate to Severe Patients With Pemphigus With the Monoclonal Anti CD20 Antibody Rituximab at a Protocol of 1000mgX2 and Assessment of Their Immune Status Via the Cylex Test</official_title>
