  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether Rituximab, in the same doses as used in
      rheumatoid arthritis patients, will benefit pemphigus patients. It also tests immune function
      via the Cylex assay in pemphigus patients before and after treatment with RItuximab.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
